What you need to know:

After two decades in the ring during which he officiated blood-spattered bouts in Kenya Novices, Intermediate, Kenya Open and National Boxing League events at Ndenderu Boxing Hall, top referee is eyeing the big stageOfficiating such tough bouts has not been in vain as it has cemented his reputation as a cool referee who is destined to become an esteemed figure in the world of boxingLast year, he was recognised by the Boxing Federation of Kenya (BFK) when he was named the top referee